headline: Can Lululemon Stock Reach $500 in 2025?
summary: Lululemon Athletica (NASDAQ: LULU) has not had a good year, to say the least.  While the S&P 500 has climbed 27% in 2024 (as of Dec. 12), the premium athleisure brand has seen its shares head in the opposite direction.  As of this writing, this consumer discretionary stock has slumped 23% in 2024 as well as from its peak about a year ago.
